sentences.en: How we conceptualize things has a lot to do with what we feel.

sentences.en: Complex processes are essentially the hard rules to conceptualize.
sentences.cn: 复杂流程实质上是一些难以概念化的规则。

sentences.en: Business Process Execution semantics are difficult to conceptualize.
sentences.cn: 业务过程执行语义很难概念化。
